title: Children's Fantasy Ebook Kindle - Daffadors: Rivalry
description:
Children's Fantasy Novel

David McKreedy, a fourth grader with amnesia, discovers that he's a powerful king from another planet. Several years earlier, he stopped his triplet brothers from taking over the universe. Now, they've escaped eternal imprisonment and are up to their old schemes. With the help of his talking dog and a team of his classmates, known as the Daffadors, David fights against his brothers' new intergalactic war.
